## Log

2026-07-15  Scaffolded. No work started.
2026-07-15  source wip. Sourced early, as part of one 02/03/04 fan out. Sourcing early is not the
            same as starting the build: the gate still stands, and 03 does not build until 02's
            verify passes. Front loading only surfaces the real risk (a project with no verifiable
            source) before the build is sunk into it. Hunting a free published sequence of operation
            with STATED TIMER VALUES: TDNE, TDES, TDEN, TDEC, neutral delay, plus voltage and
